= VimLint: A correctness and sanity checker of vim configuration.

VimLint is a tool to check your Vim configuration for poorly set options with
reasons why they're considered bad and suggestions on how to improve them.

== Quick Start

Once installed, run VimLint by doing:

  :VimLint

This will generate and open a report of your current Vim configuration.

